{"tid":2431742,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"日日睇財經台真係好撚過癮","createTime":"2021-03-04T00:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T01:57:36.000Z","uid":14090,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"802c44c0a46fbf51652911f2ae784df4295301df","tid":2431742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:55:34.000Z","msg":"日頭玩港女就靜啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完咗港女到盤前就成班把口食咗屎屎咁臭 好搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話今晚爆升 盤前升咁多 今晚升幾多 之後又話美債點 又爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後又問清倉撚係邊 又開個post話清倉撚有冇生不如死感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗準備開市 成班好撚high 情緒好高漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知high唔夠一個鐘 就話回少少姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再過多一陣就開始死老豆咁款 再繼續屌牛市契媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班SH派個頭又唔撚驚 另一邊廂就叫哂春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 跌咪啱哂你囉 比你加倉 你又驚到死唔敢加 又唔敢止蝕<br />\n<br />\n跟住呢個時候清倉派又出嚟威 話無股一身輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n瞓醒再睇啦 又話股災<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再屌契媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 財經台真係好快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389ab438888e06b97dd6ccedc96af743eb4b6e4b","tid":2431742,"uid":98813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"連登情緒指標世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45893e6137a1ae9c6d6d8c7d9544f97dbfe31cb6","tid":2431742,"uid":14090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"389ab438888e06b97dd